            <p>The game consists of two opposing teams (I see them as two opposing armies with their Generals—the Quarterbacks—involved in herculean struggles for possession of ground, similar to the effort needed for arm wrestling) towards a "Touchdown" in the opposition team's end zone (ENEMY INVASION).</p>

